62387,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T02:42:30.000Z","msg":"0:01 / 25:02<br />\n<br />\n【堅離地傾．沈旭暉 010】亂世中，如何做良心公務員？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OPDISL3b5HU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOPDISL3b5HU&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJronGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=7c6d724b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OPDISL3b5HU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n堅離地球 &middot; 沈旭暉<br />\n111K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n香港進入大黑暗時期，各行各業無不要面對「新常態」，包括香港全體公務員。究竟要當一個良心公務員，可以如何自處？在過去一年，組織公務員罷工集會公投的新公務員工會主席顏武周備受壓力，明知道可預見的風險，依然無怨無悔，經歷了哪些心路歷程？我們也邀請了曾為曾俊華助選的前AO Kennon，比較兩代公務員文化的差異。在新香港，受到打壓的都是有良心、有理想、有承擔的時代精英，同路人好應該互相扶持，直到光復一天。<br />\n<br />\nSimon 沈旭暉 堅離地 Social Media ▶<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJronGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=cf827d49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsimon.diplo...&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJronGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=542398e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...</a><br />\nPatreon: <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/simonshen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fsimonshen&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJronGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=8e5669b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/simonshen</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/simonshen_glos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsimonshen_glos&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJronGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=80ad3baf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/simonshen_glos</a><br />\nBlog: <a hre